Description: Fragment of pottery amphora, handle; black glaze on top and lower part of underside; surface worn. Hard, fine, orange clay, Munsell 2.5YR 6/6 (light red).
Bibliographic references: Weber 2012 / Untersuchungen zur archaischen griechischen Keramik aus anderen ägyptischen Fundorten (TD 346)
Acquisition notes: Found unregistered in the Department in 2010, in a box with other sherds from Tell Dafana.
